HEADWORD: Hardiment
<hw>Har"di*ment</hw> <pr>(-m⟦eit⟧nt)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OF.
<ets>hardement</ets>. See <er>Hardy</er>.]</ety> <def>Hardihood;
